  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK335">
<l>nācceṟṟu vikkuṇmēl vārāmu ṉalviṉai</l>
<l>mēṟceṉṟu ceyyap paṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let virtuous deeds be done quickly, before the biccup comes making the tongue silent.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
